            <lg xml:id="TK1036">
<l>uḻaviṉār kaimmaṭaṅki ṉillai viḻaivatūum </l>
<l>viṭṭēmeṉ pārkku nilai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the farmer's hands are slackened, even the ascetic state will fail.</l>
